      "body": "nit: I think instead of a branch, this can be a plain `ConsumeTime` call with just the `min` adjusted to go further back. This makes the fuzz format a bit more static, and the fuzz engine should still be able to figure out the edge case. You may also extend the input space by allowing time further back than one `MAX_FUTURE_BLOCK_TIME`?",
